<br>
me         &quot;ok, up button is forward, lets see if we can get wet.&quot;<br>
me         &quot;ok.... I'm in the water..whats this new bar thingy?&quot;<br>
roomie     &quot; hmm, it says here thats your air.&quot;<br>
me          &quot;ok, hmm, how do i get out of the water now?&quot;<br>
roomie     &quot;try hitting the up button&quot;<br>
me          &quot;I did, but that is forward, whats the book say?&quot;<br>
roomie     &quot; lets see....&quot;<br>
me         &quot; wait, whats it doing now.. whats this &quot;Loading, Please wait&quot; thing? I cant move? is the computer frozen?&quot;<br>
roomie &quot; that means its my turn&quot;<br>
n00bie 101. =)<br>
<br>
My second death was 15 minutes later when a gyrl in the dorm who gamed stoped by. She told me to go up to one of the gaurd people and hit &quot;A&quot; for advice if I had any game questions.<br>
<br>
