<br>
Loading, please wait...<br>
<br>
And thus I learned that some creatures are &quot;social&quot; and will add when you attack their brethren.<br>
<br>
My second character (twink) fared much better, as I had him well equipped (by my standards in those days) with my clerics hand me down banded, and a blackened alloy LS. He didn't die once until he got to lvl 9 or so, and the group I had just joined decided we had enough manpower to break a full camp at orc one.<br>
<br>
Of course my favorite early death was still the time my cleric  (about lvl 14) was paired up with a lvl 17 or so pally, killing dervs at derv one. &lt;me&gt;&quot;Hey who's this Dorn B'dynn guy&quot;? &lt;the pally&gt;&quot;Dunno, but he cons blue to me&quot;(or maybe it was even) &quot;lets give him a try&quot;<br>
<br>
Healing pally001<br>
Healing pally001...<br>
etc.<br>
OOM<br>
Pally down to 2 bubbles, I start running for the efp zone. Made it to the edge of the green area (on the freeport side), before he killed me. <br>
